headline: ISRG Q2 Deep Dive: New Platform Drives Procedure Growth Amid Global Expansion
summary: Medical technology company Intuitive Surgical (NASDAQ:ISRG) reported Q2 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 21.4% year on year to $2.44 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.19 per share was 14.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Can ISRG's Strong Q2 Procedure Volume Translate Into Durable EPS Upside?
summary: ISRG's Q2 procedure growth hits 17%, but continuation of EPS growth hinges on easing margin pressure from FX and da Vinci 5 adoption.
